               stealing three brilliant diamond hair pins, value 20 l. one pair of brilliant diamond earrings, value 30 l. one gold locket with a silver bow-knot set with brilliant diamonds, value 5 l. one pair of plain gold drop ear-rings, value 20 s. and a hair necklace with a gold buckle and gold end, value 10 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17780916-10-victim109" type="victimName">
